title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Party with Carnival Gifts
content:
Celebrate Carnival on the streets of Los Santos. Play GTA Online anytime through March 3 and your character will receive the Carnival Feather Shirt and Shorts for men, or get the Carnival Feather Dress and the Carnival Sun Dress for women.

Uncork a bottle of champagne at any bar to obtain the Carnival Neck Gaiter.
